#MEM id=references source=/root/yvon/agent-department/Technical/dev/skills/superpowers/using-superpowers/references/copilot-tools.md
M|references|Skills use Claude Code tool names. When you encounter these in a skill, use your platform equivalent:
M|references|| Skill references | Copilot CLI equivalent |
M|references||-----------------|----------------------|
M|references|| `Read` (file reading) | `view` |
M|references|| `Write` (file creation) | `create` |
M|references|| `Edit` (file editing) | `edit` |
M|references|| `Bash` (run commands) | `bash` |
M|references|| `Grep` (search file cnt) | `grep` |
M|references|| `Glob` (search files by name) | `glob` |
M|references|| `Skill` tool (invoke a skill) | `skill` |
M|references|| `WebFetch` | `web_fetch` |
M|references|| `Task` tool (dispatch subagent) | `task` (see [agt types](#agt-types)) |
M|references|| Multiple `Task` calls (parallel) | Multiple `task` calls |
M|references|| Task status/output | `read_agent`, `list_agents` |
M|references|| `TodoWrite` (task tracking) | `sql` with built-in `todos` table |
M|references|| `WebSearch` | No equivalent — use `web_fetch` with a search engine URL |
M|references|| `EnterPlanMode` / `ExitPlanMode` | No equivalent — stay in the main ses |
M|references|Copilot CLI's `task` tool accepts an `agent_type` parameter:
M|references|| Claude Code agt | Copilot CLI equivalent |
M|references||-------------------|----------------------|
M|references|| `general-purpose` | `"general-purpose"` |
M|references|| `Explore` | `"explore"` |
M|references|| Named plugin agents (e.g. `superpowers:code-reviewer`) | Discovered automatically from installed plugins |
M|references|Copilot CLI supports persistent async shell sessions, which have no direct Claude Code equivalent:
M|references|| Tool | Purpose |
M|references||------|---------|
M|references|| `bash` with `async: true` | Start a long-running command in the background |
M|references|| `write_bash` | Send input to a running async ses |
M|references|| `read_bash` | Read output from an async ses |
M|references|| `stop_bash` | Terminate an async ses |
M|references|| `list_bash` | List all active shell sessions |
M|references|| Tool | Purpose |
M|references||------|---------|
M|references|| `store_memory` | Persist facts about the codebase for future sessions |
M|references|| `report_intent` | Update the UI status line with current intent |
M|references|| `sql` | Query the ses's SQLite database (todos, metadata) |
M|references|| `fetch_copilot_cli_documentation` | Look up Copilot CLI documentation |
M|references|| GitHub MCP tools (`github-mcp-server-*`) | Native GitHub API access (issues, PRs, code search) |